{"word":"μανία","slug":"μανία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μανία</b></el> <el>(μανία, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μαίνομαι'><el>μαίνομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>madness, frenzy</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>enthusiasm, inspired frenzy</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>mad passion, fury</i>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}